    {
      "name": "cancel_funding",
      "docs": [
        "Admin aborts a funding round that won't reach soft cap. Sets the",
        "is_cancelled flag, blocking further deposits and `execute_facility`.",
        "Lenders pull their USDC back via the existing `withdraw_funding`",
        "(which already requires `!is_active`, true for a cancelled pool).",
        "One-way: a cancelled pool cannot be revived; admin must initialize",
        "a new facility_id."
      ],
